This paper discusses a new training method for neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The proposed method is tested on benchmark datasets, which suggests it could also fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of more parameters to improve model fitting, which could also relate to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category.
